---
/**
 * Trust.astro
 * Section highlighting energy efficiency of local inference
 */
---

<section class="py-24 bg-rice-paper relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
            <!-- Content -->
            <div class="space-y-8">
                <h2
                    class="font-heading font-black text-4xl md:text-5xl text-charcoal-ink"
                >
                    A smaller footprint, by design.
                </h2>

                <div class="prose prose-lg text-charcoal-ink/90 font-body">
                    <p>
                        Running AI locally on your Mac isn’t just private—it’s
                        sustainable. By eliminating the need for constant data
                        center processing, BonsAI dramatically lowers the energy
                        cost of every interaction.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <ul
                    class="space-y-4 font-mono text-sm border-t-2 border-charcoal-ink/10 pt-8"
                >
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                        <span
                            class="w-2 h-2 bg-olive-growth rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0"
                        ></span>
                        <span>No data center overhead</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                        <span
                            class="w-2 h-2 bg-olive-growth rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0"
                        ></span>
                        <span>Zero network transmission energy</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                        <span
                            class="w-2 h-2 bg-olive-growth rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0"
                        ></span>
                        <span>Optimized for Apple Silicon efficiency</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <!-- Visual: Big percentage callout -->
            <div class="relative">
                <div
                    class="absolute -top-4 -right-4 w-32 h-32 bg-olive-growth/10 rounded-full blur-3xl z-0"
                >
                </div>
                <div
                    class="relative z-10 bg-white border-2 border-charcoal-ink shadow-base p-10 text-center"
                >
                    <div
                        class="w-32 h-32 bg-olive-growth/5 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6"
                    >
                        <svg
                            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                            fill="none"
                            stroke="currentColor"
                            stroke-width="1.5"
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-linejoin="round"
                            class="w-16 h-16 text-olive-growth"
                        >
                            <path
                                d="M11 20A7 7 0 0 1 9.8 6.1C15.5 5 17 4.48 19 2c1 2 2 4.18 2 8 0 5.5-4.78 10-10 10Z"
                            ></path>
                            <path
                                d="M2 21c0-3 1.85-5.36 5.08-6C9.5 14.52 12 13 13 12"
                            ></path>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <p class="font-heading text-2xl text-charcoal-ink mt-4">
                        Lower Energy
                    </p>
                    <p class="font-mono text-sm text-charcoal-ink/60 mt-2">
                        vs. Cloud Models
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
